<li><a href="http://www.brennancenter.org/stack_detail.asp?key=97&amp;subkey=38150&amp;init_key=105" class="external text" title="http://www.brennancenter.org/stack_detail.asp?key=97&amp;subkey=38150&amp;init_key=105" rel="nofollow">The Machinery of Democracy: Voting System Security, Accessibility, Usability, and Cost</a> from <a href="/wiki/Brennan_Center_for_Justice" title="Brennan Center for Justice">Brennan Center for Justice</a> at the <a href="/wiki/New_York_University_Law_School" title="New York University Law School" class="mw-redirect">New York University Law School</a></li>
