<li><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=90727541" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=90727541" rel="nofollow">NPR</a> summary of current technology status in the states of the U.S., as of May 2008.</li>
</ul>


